    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or a donor for parts. The engine starts but suffers from a persistent misfire and significant exhaust smoke, suggesting internal wear. The body has several deep dents and visible rust on the rocker panels, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. It currently requires a jump start to turn over and will likely need to be towed to its new home.",
      "price": 4000.0,
